OL,6,GTonight's much-publicised edition of
OL,7,GPanorama ` revealing evidence of
OL,8,Gracism and misogyny at one of London's
OL,9,Gbusiest police stations, Charing Cross
OL,10,G` was disrupted by a playout error.
OL,12,FThe programme was in its final minutes
OL,13,Fwhen (for viewers in England and
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland), a trail for BBC
OL,15,FRadio 3 Unwind suddenly appeared.
OL,17,FA BBC One breakdown slide appeared
OL,18,Fbriefly before we cut to the output
OL,19,Ffrom one of the BBC Sport galleries in
OL,20,FSalford, which was due to air a live
OL,21,Ftrail in the junction prior to the
OL,22,F10pm news.
