OL,6,FAnd it's not the first time Panorama
OL,7,Fhas been impacted by a playout issue.
OL,8,FAn edition of the programme was
OL,9,Fdelayed by twelve minutes in November
OL,10,F2020, again due to human error at Red
OL,11,FBee.
OL,13,FPlayout of BBC One in Northern
OL,14,FIreland, Scotland and Wales is handled
OL,15,Fby in-house teams in each of the
OL,16,Frespective nations, though London's
OL,17,Foutput is seen there for much of the
OL,18,Fday.
OL,20,FStaff in Belfast, Glasgow and Cardiff
OL,21,Fintervened during the breakdown:
