OL,7,F Northern Ireland took London's
OL,8,Foutput for the in-programme breakdown.
OL,9,FBut Belfast Playout intervened to
OL,10,Fprevent the post-programme breakdown
OL,11,F(seen in the rest of the country) and
OL,12,Fseamlessly filled with trails up to
OL,13,Fthe 10pm news.
OL,14,F Glasgow was in-circuit when the
OL,15,Fbreakdown occurred and so when London
OL,16,Finadvertently triggered the next
OL,17,Fjunction, Scottish viewers initially
OL,18,Fsaw the BBC logo and music usually
OL,19,Fplayed out on the clean feed of BBC
OL,20,FOne during junctions.Scotland put the
OL,21,FSalford Sport studio to air for
OL,22,Fslightly longer than Network before
OL,23,Fcutting up their own breakdown
OL,24,Fgraphic. The Scottish announcer
OL,25,Fprovided a verbal apology.BBC One
